{
  "texts": [
    "He also holds a Specialist degree in Instructional Design from Instituto de Desenho Instrucional.",
    "In his Master's degree research, he designed, implemented and evaluated two translation courses (in-person and distance learning) on translation hermeneutics.",
    "He was a Lecturer at the Western Paraná State University, teaching English language teachers, Tourism and Hospitality undergraduates.",
    "Currently, he is a PhD student funded by the School of Applied Languages and Intercultural Studies (SALIS) in Dublin City University.",
    "His PhD project aims to design, implement and evaluate training on human evaluation of Machine Translation to Master's NLP students."
  ]
}